commit.message:
Properly escape text injected into regex

Because I was not previously escaping text inteserted into the regex, a
"." was added instead of "\.", so it let ANYTHING pass. BAD.

Add tests to challenge de locale

These tests make sure the locale number formatting regex works
correctly.

Include a test for issue #109

This test highlights the bug, and its presence ensures it does not occur
again.

Disable windows testing

choco is failing for some reason, so I cannot test on Windows
